<P>Being &s;uch as Graduates by Prefer|ment, at fir&s;t nam'd by the Founder; and after the fir&s;t Settlement to be cho&s;en out of the Fir&s;t or Second Col|lege; with Apartments in the Col|lege, and Salaries.</P>
