<P>The <HI>General</HI> to be nam'd by the Founder, out of the <HI>Collonels;</HI> the <HI>Col|lonels</HI> to be nam'd by the <HI>General,</HI> out of the <HI>Captains;</HI> the <HI>Captains</HI> out of the <HI>Governors;</HI> the <HI>Governors</HI> from the <HI>Directors,</HI> and the <HI>Directors</HI> from the <HI>Exempts,</HI> and &s;o on.</P>
